title: Fed's Williams Calls Powell a Man of 'Impeccable Integrity'
description: Federal Reserve Bank of New York President John Williams says Fed Chair Jerome Powell is completely dedicated to the central bank's mission during a Council on Foreign Relations event in New York. (Source: Bloomberg)
